r provided with an engaging seat, and is introduced in such a way that in case of exposure to a temperature lower than a preset critical threshold temperature (T<sub>c</sub>), the filiform shape memory member performs a phase transition, causing an irreversible disengagement condition visible through a transparent window.</p></abstract></us-patent-application>